<!--
	CAU HINH PET
	- Limitation: Gioi han
		- MaxCanTake: So luong pet toi da co the mang theo
		- MaxLevel: Cap do toi da
		- MaxSkill: So luong ky nang toi da
		- MaxJoy: So diem vui ve toi da
		- MaxLife: So diem tuoi tho toi da
	- Base: Thong tin co ban
		- BaseAttackSkillID: ID ky nang danh thuong co ban
		- LevelUpRemainPoints: So diem tiem nang cong them moi khi len cap
		- DieLoseLife: So diem tuoi tho mat khi chet
		- CallFightRequireJoyOver: Xuat chien yeu cau phai co toi thieu bao nhieu diem vui ve
		- CallFightRequireLifeOver: Xuat chien yeu cau phai co toi thieu bao nhieu diem tuoi tho
		- CallFightCostJoy: Xuat chien tieu hao bao nhieu diem vui ve
		- SubJoyInterval: Thoi gian moi khoang se giam do vui ve cua tinh linh di 1 diem (mili-giay)
		- OwnerExpP: % kinh nghiem nhan duoc tu chu nhan khi giet quai
	- Items: Danh sach vat pham chuc nang
		- ResetAttributesItemID: ID vat pham tay diem tiem nang
		- SkillStudyMedicineItemID: ID vat pham linh hoi dan
	- Feed: Thong tin cac vat pham chuc nang
		- Joyful: Do vui ve
			- Item: Thong tin vat pham
				- ItemID: ID vat pham
				- Point: So diem tang them
		- Life: Tuoi tho
			- Item: Thong tin vat pham
				- ItemID: ID vat pham
				- Point: So diem tang them
		- Enlightenment: Linh ngo
			- Item: Thong tin vat pham
				- ItemID: ID vat pham
				- Point: So diem tang them
	- ExpList: Danh sach kinh nghiem thang cap theo cap do danh dau tu 1
		- Value: Gia tri kinh nghiem yeu cau
	- Scrolls: Danh sach sach ky nang
		- Scroll: Thong tin sach
			- ItemID: ID vat pham sach
			- SkillID: ID ky nang se hoc duoc
	- SkillLevelUp: Thong tin thang cap ky nang
		- LevelUpData: Thong tin thang cap (danh so tu 1)
			- Rate: Ty le %
			- RequireEnlightenment: So diem linh ngo yeu cau
	- SkillStudyRates: Danh sach ty le hoc duoc ky nang moi theo cap do hien tai cua ky nang (danh so tu 0), neu hong se de len ky nang bat ky hien co
		- Data: Du lieu
			- StudyNewRate: Ty le hoc moi (%)
-->
